a004da354b6c3f4c4e7a2a996a69eac9c¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬Cemetery¬aab3e86d8987f7138a99118e5cde6a351¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a02f80d9ed02677e224b9043082107272¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬RealEstateAgent¬ad12f85113f6b6c985f0dcb918f4804fb¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a066804a3756d5e499d551edfce9e8330¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬Plumber¬ad7f84261f6b72a313ea1d6f3e76b95c1¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a085dc8efd4e7a740cacab9ec239311ef¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬CivicStructure¬a57fd29349a4406e62fc2a4b0dfa22bdb¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a0be35b0ee38f8036cebfb9c4e8ff005d¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬PlaceOfWorship¬aa584c25c7b72c1bc4329b86ef7d5edff¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a10e19c7607df83ed251a1a787557a84d¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. a15a58c6d93476c24c5dd59498f3bf524¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬Bakery¬a84c7a2d64be8ad148d9c33ab52680a5f¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a163b7ce449e42d95420934c0a7869894¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬TaxiStand¬a09502bb7fc9c7f6a6b933ecb20e17433¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a1d72c09efa8f8cf17bfa0a9939b8540d¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬Beach¬ad1b5b8e4208946ec82168c28211353eb¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a1f0b2a4ccee12d1e090b4e34bf26b467¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬FastFoodRestaurant¬a8c40b904948705073a259c3a9aaa43ba¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a222c171dd23e735902600987bdb72021¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬Motel¬a5507c3450e0295464a1333a2dd23dc0e¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a25fe88cff18fca8597eb1d6e68b30d80¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬PetStore¬a3e8ac54222c5f8f001a9f961d082394a¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a2918120b574e33e60ce6e810fe194809¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬CafeOrCoffeeShop¬a2c444d1de0a2120139da04da9a517f7f¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a29b4186a7716033db9485f0d67038076¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬MedicalClinic¬a6327c182c9f1b076e6aea686b4f63167¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a2e084f8742ec612c25fb88408439673e¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬Crematorium¬afc8794214a72111f505b855c40e77231¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a31ca7ac90cfd42f867b47d9b263138fc¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬AutoDealer¬aa5516a57b60250ca06a7d93322cd22c1¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a3409a3f6415082d7e3d59477101ac316¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬PawnShop¬adfd823b8970a8b40e47e42c4a380acde¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a3609895db1b7e142e5c78b7d2c6d79ee¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬DryCleaningOrLaundry¬a6fc6b6e0781cefceaf918a01369e0613¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a38c29725958640ad3e3148d599179645¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬Zoo¬a234734e00c4b38920e23c2c32887d45b¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬Casino¬a842f99db795cd8d79c34f42902d74f4a¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬CityHall¬a2a6c3999edfc0d1b088eacf48f52a458¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a45fad195814c5fbc3357df2ee3b00a8c¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬LocalBusiness¬a86b39b73e4ba6ed3b8fdf231300cc3ec¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a4953480f5c5766b8c76394ec0bab7aac¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬HealthAndBeautyBusiness¬a9cb6529f02007298121b980d40cea2ec¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a4a92a344bddbf2963d60c2a7fe3ed084¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬Museum¬a70a5eff2cfdadfbabf2b648512299f39¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a4dfb92f5a919de03367b01a4bcdc1401¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬SportsActivityLocation¬a4976e7d10f0aef98bcef913dbfa8aaa8¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a51065911637b0499cfab9ef4f1b1ede8¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬MovieRentalStore¬a6a986b2c704d05a9a6c8958ec302119c¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a529605823f91e81b0cfb997c371566a7¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬ProfessionalService¬a9ab8bae5861f882db2be1bb69c19b279¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a57dc363b8fc65ebe12be00cd6f18cd53¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬Campground¬a4248be3f1d69008e95b102374f62b7f3¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a5e5fcaf2d1bd0bfbcbc6f3a10834caa9¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬AutoBodyShop¬a6ee0ab2f16a65ba80ca90fa5248c1c2e¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a611df74a52ade8db2ef3aabbd11478ab¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬SportsClub¬a3c927d121a7ded4536e8c6a3e5d90bbe¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a62f303309d9c95e7dce5bc26033cf20a¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬Attorney¬a5dda950cd882b35f89d6681d9fab0794¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a6608e5f97277aa4b9e34c8c26e951fda¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬GasStation¬a5f1c57deee9c3f12208e33e2ced11c8f¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a6a6e694a76e3a4f8b714dde490f02f46¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬Playground¬a08b96aa8dc0e5773e5032b0feb9884dd¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a707b18d8f97730bbceb316a946fae9ab¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬ConvenienceStore¬a9196a01bc91a3bb4834e28228753667e¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a71c5ba94b22b3611af5a2edcdc932b83¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬GovernmentBuilding¬abf112ec4dc53deabf0979485c99ac051¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a7532fd3b952273c6c57819d4b5bf9628¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬Courthouse¬a5909fca2a9ebb128cc9d7abd2a151488¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a7ab67ffb3a73a7aead6505b07fa44088¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬DepartmentStore¬aa04f49710c220932d5fe94f406272192¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a822498bed52a93d2238bf034a3cccfb0¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬MobilePhoneStore¬aeeecdf66855e07d04c4689358ffa5e37¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a84b7db3ef77aebcabf9b6b9ef09dace6¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬GeneralContractor¬ac47256077c152fb66e0fb9bc00cfa5c4¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a8a3dbe55998ee08c44eb24450c982a24¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬AutoWash¬a9265f22bd0416a8971f109846143cda0¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a90042874effbad21397a192c9c9e7a93¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬AccountingService¬a68eb286852405a28e36563eea83f8642¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a9204e8dfa0afb5ea3b9fe107671a24db¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬ParkingFacility¬a70382940d47360f4dde0c73cfb599963¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a93397a9b11dcd852f94b82990711fa7e¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬DaySpa¬aad4282c1dfbaba2eaa3fb658369aa7ea¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a96dc5dce03d0c6bf8f50214e65fafb4e¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬Electrician¬afecba37685a0352f92261f9710947185¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a9ca0e54ec649127a65ed01506fdd2762¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬Notary¬a1a185de6da4e426d34553a4326cfcb07¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬BookStore¬a18d52e4f13974cf2d002dcbd90058570¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

aa3540b45fc53c84e1ba814f9bf6bcddd¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬RecyclingCenter¬a361ec659fc773e0f70907654de4ee9ca¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

aa5d277c03092956a332a1cdd76cabf9e¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬MusicStore¬ab60f7e36a966c74fa6cdcc0d9076741d¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

aa880a17a0593791297c82bad872044ab¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬Synagogue¬a082f94d2c6a4f4eb2178526e9bac2c36¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

aadf72694cb6d187bfe9b21a5e1267dca¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬TrainStation¬ad53103969be6be625cb5303405ba5ef8¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

aaf96728f33440d466be4e2f2075462cd¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬JewelryStore¬accd5d3020b709e5e7305c9e584fd427b¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

ab2d3107f488a06795f7f9d9e69035673¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬BowlingAlley¬a29cd10bc94f06f63a80ac078c08fb742¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

ab6e6515cc4128174a701bbfd2060c54d¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬SkiResort¬a4bdaf814f3a42b5a6f2f9a2d5b97f5ae¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

ab9454e8b98da575151e984b507f67f66¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬TouristInformationCenter¬a270495c00ce42a795bd3c84f7f7214a7¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

abb9fa458b24e19ccc28ce6cefd496372¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬BusStop¬abf851455f2f85620e7573ac22942f697¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

abe402f84399f86bfb19574d297ea95a7¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬EventVenue¬add378c1c6d0f296b5b6d1893ba497163¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

ac1172170a0606861d1142483f9459b03¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬HomeAndConstructionBusiness¬a0d482fbd4537086c52250002add8a783¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

ac5a13fe2ec4a4a0bb1bd2eead70aed33¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬TennisComplex¬adf59cf4e1d8444fe259c493f2030bf00¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

ac6f1bf8440bfe35a3348ed4aca6b5cdb¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬HairSalon¬a321dfba6d3ed33fa139fc4c61df9a48c¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

aca7ef298c5abf3969ec1ec3c4f9266de¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬MedicalOrganization¬a8d4fad333591c90b1dc46ddc57570ad2¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

ad1bc57a4b1309f91f5f33b163ce7a153¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬MotorcycleRepair¬a7e2db890fb5dbc140ba9075621ea5afc¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

ad427d0a99f5dfe353f68b44fd1d12101¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬ShoppingCenter¬ac6f482e6dbff1fea27840605afca0bbc¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

ad64a126941737a8e4fc38afb1fa87d1a¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬ComedyClub¬adf12b957667ed0867ea642adaa6339e4¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

ad823eed5b72ba86c5db6237dce49ee0a¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬NightClub¬a686c223580916fed0f3e5cdf723b468f¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

adc8e9d71b7eb9cb4979e5695a90c3680¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬LegislativeBuilding¬a3a31179edce7defb773344b9f6185470¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

adf2bf2ea2e9e7dd5f298f91b9f80d974¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬CivicStructure¬DefenceEstablishment¬a26c67bf5fd59f46ab44cb55e7782ef62¬15¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

ae02a4c99a18bc10b792f303cf31a184d¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬PoliceStation¬a370eab4364d2f5523620ffad5042a7b4¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

ae4088851053c7c03af5ad0400e7faca4¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬HealthClub¬a229fd28b49745046efbd1ed8c6098eb2¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

ae687b600f7aa756fb64fb8ba3b579913¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬AdultEntertainment¬ac81f80f0b214ca6d2e3bdc36bd417afc¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

aec6d71f92f48bad7c200eb3712064548¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬Hotel¬a1c0f40e0ce1d218cd4529c126cd03b6a¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

aef5fb34ae2e729de02841a14852fa70c¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬AutomatedTeller¬a719331db427bca67d0c1d64372c38d06¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

af0be57723f5c3c3ce3cf6701717e03df¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬LiquorStore¬aabc91c637ab06d3ae101a754f4ca6ae5¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

af356136e0a59cb559439ab1493498417¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬AutoPartsStore¬a286c1902ffcea6352aab30b85cbf2330¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

af6ca7c6ad162875a2d20fcf26a633966¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬ComputerStore¬a08cd5bcfec33a12b87499cfd1043c0c0¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

af99d1e4f3c040165f1e25dcacc000335¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬HousePainter¬acd622f5473c65cb522920a30ded34ba1¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

affd2fba3f0b84cfb88a6640d1369e10d¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬Pharmacy¬a1dd591cccae92ae8f901e2b99607a3df¬24¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a706b4e1109b1ef712f919206ea61e747¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬Hospital¬a751e00475e037ed618c774c9a95e65fc¬1000¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a711ae9bb0593954246ad9c92f7621a44¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬RoofingContractor¬ab92e05bd5c7f4aa6748188c4f87906c6¬1000¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

a621f8c78acee6419cecfb13e4aeeb0ac¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬HousePainter¬a034702db36aca958122b6a341b5a1ac7¬1000¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

ac777444a48c21ca80f4d54f34ddb487c¬openingHours¬Opening Hours¬Duration¬¬Duration¬Text field¬The opening hours for a business. Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬Dentist¬a9e07587fed4bf250e084beb89cfaf1f8¬1000¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. Day or time ranges are specified using a hyphen '-'.- Days are specified using the following two-letter combinations: Mo, Tu, We, Th, Fr, Sa, Su.- Times are specified using 24:00 time. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬AccountingService¬a37e5b3db8538e78fa7598b2a82959b96¬1000¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0

Opening hours can be specified as a weekly time range, starting with days, then times per day. Multiple days can be listed with commas ',' separating each day. For example, 3pm is specified as 15:00. - Here is an example: &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Tu,Th 16:00-20:00&quot;&gt;Tuesdays and Thursdays 4-8pm&lt;/time&gt;. - If a business is open 7 days a week, then it can be specified as &lt;time itemprop=&quot;openingHours&quot; datetime=&quot;Mo-Su&quot;&gt;Monday through Sunday, all day&lt;/time&gt;.¬¬LocalBusiness¬AutoPartsStore¬a78c2df030486aee387a05b289b7351c1¬1000¬1¬1¬0¬0¬0¬0¬¬0
